data.description: Spacious ranch with one large bedroom and one regular bedroom.  New washer, furnace, and central air.  Eating area in the kitchen.  Private fenced in yard with 1.5 car garage. Nice location in the midst of Garden City with plenty of shopping in the immediate area.
